high_descs: open up the cabinet to the left of the microwave and get out a cup
bring the cup over to the kitchen stove
place the cup in the microwave above the kitchen stove and turn it on, then take out the cup
take the cup over to the three brown shelves in the corner of the kitchen
place the cup on the top shelf
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved cup on the brown shelf

high_descs: Go to the cabinet behind you.
Remove the cup from the cabinet.
Take the cup to the microwave next to the cabinet.
Heat the cup in the microwave.
Take the cup to the shelf behind you and to the right.
Place the cup on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated cup on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and move towards the refrigerator then turn left and move to the toaster next to the oven.
Open the cabinet door above the toaster, pick up the gold cup, and then close the cabinet.
Turn right and move to towards the oven then turn right and face the oven.
Open the microwave above the oven, microwave the gold cup, open the microwave again and pick up the gold cup.

Turn left and move towards the wall then turn left again and move towards the refrigerator, then turn right and move towards the door, and finally turn left and move to the shelves in the corner of the room.
Place the gold cup on the right side of the shelves' top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated cup on a shelf.
